  "_README": "Declares reusable image assets for image-based quizzes. Run `node quizzes/assets/fetch-assets.mjs` to download them into icons/ and monuments/. The site references LOCAL paths only. Quiz generators (quizzes/tools/) build questions ONLY from assets that actually downloaded, so missing slugs never produce broken entries. See README.md for licensing.",

